"from their names.  <placeholder type=\"footnote\" id=\"0\"/> There are few "
"notable ones worth making (over)simplified explanation here assuming typical "
"build environment based on <filename>Makefile</filename>.  <placeholder type="
"\"footnote\" id=\"1\"/>"
