#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><para>
msgid ""
"If you encounter an upload problem at <ulink url=\"&uploadqueue;\"/>, you "
"can fix this by manually uploading GPG signed <filename>*.commands</"
"filename> file to there with <command>ftp</command>.  <placeholder type="
"\"footnote\" id=\"0\"/> For example, use <filename>hello.commands</filename>:"
